dialog.attr1: Man... they really botched this one.
I know you are supposed to be ugly... but that's another level.
Going to make the world more beautiful by killing you.
Wish I could wipe the memory of you.
Weak, who you were! Weak, who you are!
You? You couldn't even die right.
I'll be doing the former you a favor.
Whatever you got in exchange... I'm sure it was wasted.
You make me wish they'd have taken both my eyes...
